    <briefdescription>
<para>Stores parent-child relationships for hierarchical entity graphs. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1core_1_1ecs_1_1components_1_1HierarchyComponent" kindref="compound">HierarchyComponent</ref> enables entities to form tree structures where state changes (e.g., activation, transformation) can propagate from parent to child entities. The dirty flag signals that the hierarchy has changed and needs propagation.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>THandle</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The entity handle type used for parent/child references. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
